{
  "stem": "166.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was like wet, and it was-- we were sleeping on ice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Anyway, I don't know how we lived through.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It's just a miracle that we are alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The next night, they pressed us into a barn.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They pushed in so many people that it was impossible to lay down.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] It was terrible-- that march.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Then we came in to Gross-Rosen in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was about midnight, two o'clock.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And there was no room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They pushed us into a barrack where they used-- where they made-- supposed to be toilets in that barrack.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So there were ditches in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we had to-- they just pushed us in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they pressed us over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They pushed so many people in, people couldn't go in anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There was no more room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And so they're staying with whips near the door, and they start hitting.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "As soon as they start hitting-- nobody wanted to get hit, and it created self pressure.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And some people went up-- lift themselves up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And some people went down from the pressure that the people pushed themselves inside in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I was hanging in the air.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I was hanging in the air, and I couldn't move my hands like this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And the people who went down-- they were trampled to death.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They couldn't get up anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "We were staying on dead people so they pushed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "It was impossible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "That was in Gross-Rosen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "We were there then about three days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "In the middle of the night, they bring in three containers of soup.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And everybody with that little pot that he had or the dish-- please, please, please, please, please, please.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "We couldn't come to it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
